front.title: •Admiral Chiraneau
front.gametext: Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting a Star Destroyer at a battleground system, adds 1 to your Force drains here and at each other battleground system controlled by a Star Destroyer within 2 parsecs of Chiraneau.
front.lore: Deep space transmissions expert. Piett's personal advisor. TIE ace promoted upon Piett's request.
